---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="CEREC Same-Day Crowns" 
  category="Digital Dentistry"
  description="Get beautiful, durable dental restorations in just one appointment using our advanced CEREC technology."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1629909615184-74f495363b67?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Same-Day Restorations</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Using digital impressioning, we can produce realistic dental restorations – and it only takes one appointment. 
        CEREC is a great way to restore your smile if you have missing or chipped teeth, or unattractive fillings.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      What is CEREC Technology?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        CEREC (Chairside Economical Restoration of Esthetic Ceramics) is revolutionary dental technology 
        that allows us to design, create, and place custom ceramic restorations in a single visit. 
        Gone are the days of temporary crowns, multiple appointments, and waiting weeks for your restoration.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Traditional Process</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Multiple appointments</li>
            <li>• Temporary crowns</li>
            <li>• 2-3 week wait time</li>
            <li>• Messy impressions</li>
            <li>• Risk of sensitivity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">CEREC Process</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>• Single appointment</li>
            <li>• Permanent restoration same day</li>
            <li>• No waiting period</li>
            <li>• Digital impressions</li>
            <li>• Immediate function</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The CEREC Process
    </h2>

    <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Digital Scanning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We use a special 3D camera to take precise digital impressions of your tooth. 
              No messy putty impressions needed – the process is comfortable and quick.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Custom Design</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our dentist designs your restoration using advanced CAD software, ensuring 
              perfect fit, function, and aesthetics that match your natural teeth.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Precision Milling</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Your restoration is milled from a high-quality ceramic block in our office 
              using the CEREC milling machine. This process takes about 15-20 minutes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Final Placement</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We carefully place and bond your new restoration, making final adjustments 
              to ensure perfect bite and comfort. You leave with a complete, permanent restoration.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Benefits of CEREC Restorations
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Time-Saving Convenience</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Complete treatment in one appointment saves you time and multiple visits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Superior Fit</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Digital impressions ensure exceptional accuracy and comfort.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Natural Appearance</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">High-quality ceramics match your natural tooth color and translucency.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Durable Materials</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Strong ceramic restorations can last 10-15 years or more with proper care.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Metal-Free</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">All-ceramic restorations are biocompatible and mercury-free.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">No Temporary Crown</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Avoid the inconvenience and potential complications of temporary restorations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Same-Day Smile Restoration
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Don't let damaged teeth affect your confidence. With CEREC technology, you can 
        get a beautiful, permanent restoration in just one convenient appointment.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your CEREC Appointment
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/crowns-bridges" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Crowns & Bridges</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Traditional restorative options</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/dental-implants" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Implants</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Permanent tooth replacement</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/veneers" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Porcelain Veneers</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cosmetic smile enhancement</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long does a CEREC appointment take?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most CEREC appointments take 1.5 to 2 hours from start to finish. This includes preparation, 
        scanning, designing, milling, and final placement of your restoration.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Are CEREC restorations as strong as traditional crowns?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Yes! CEREC restorations are made from high-quality ceramic materials that are just as 
        strong and durable as traditional lab-made crowns. They can last 10-15 years or more 
        with proper care.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Is CEREC more expensive than traditional crowns?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        While the upfront cost may be similar, CEREC often provides better value because you save 
        time with fewer appointments and avoid the inconvenience of temporary crowns. Many patients 
        find the convenience worth the investment.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">What can CEREC be used for?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        CEREC can create crowns, inlays, onlays, and veneers. It's ideal for restoring damaged teeth, 
        replacing old fillings, and improving the appearance of chipped or discolored teeth.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>